  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU:</h1><p>      </p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/86ef49b207aa39ac2fb7614b2d7b3eb0.avif?t=1655744295\" width=600 height=109 /></span><br><br><strong>Arrange the letters</strong> and <strong>answer the questions</strong> described at the bottom.<br><strong>Very simple controls</strong>, left click to pick a piece up, mouse wheel to rotate in either direction, another left click to place.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/b791697213f5dedb53e84383e665c494.poster.avif?t=1655744295\" width=600 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/b791697213f5dedb53e84383e665c494.webm?t=1655744295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/b791697213f5dedb53e84383e665c494.mp4?t=1655744295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/115bb96ad6b21dd387ab01df2fa15960.avif?t=1655744295\" width=600 height=109 /></span><br><br>Unlock the figures and customize your luggage, <strong>making it unique!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/83b0c30a52337d0bea9642762ee37ed5.poster.avif?t=1655744295\" width=600 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/83b0c30a52337d0bea9642762ee37ed5.webm?t=1655744295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/83b0c30a52337d0bea9642762ee37ed5.mp4?t=1655744295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/896fa7fec3f9deb5907ab81e8c6f5c55.avif?t=1655744295\" width=600 height=109 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 sticks to collect<br></li><li>Designed for crosswords lovers;<br></li><li>Solve 50 puzzles carefully created;<br></li><li>Enjoy 23 beautiful landscapes;<br></li><li>Choose the level of difficulty that you want to face (Easy, Normal or Hard);<br></li><li>Original soundtrack, specially composed to help you keep your focus and concentration;<br></li><li>Everything in the game was made with a lot of love and craftsmanship;</li></ul>",
